dct_title_s: Map to illustrate the winds of North East Australia to acccompany the paper by Dr. A. Rattray M.D. R.N.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Major seasonal winds direction and airmasses shown by lines, colored bands, arrows, and text. From: the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 38 (1868), pp. 370-411; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.38 1868
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1868.
